    },
    {
      "question": "A 58-year-old bus driver believes his neighbors have installed hidden microphones in his walls to blackmail him. He has covered his walls with aluminum foil, filed police reports, but continues to work every day without problems. He has no hallucinations or disorganized behavior. Most likely diagnosis?",
      "difficulty": "application",
