      }
    },
    {
      "question": "What distinguishes schizoaffective disorder from schizophrenia with comorbid depression?",
      "difficulty": "tricky",
      "options": [
        "Schizoaffective only occurs in younger patients",
        "In schizoaffective, mood episodes are prominent features meeting full diagnostic criteria, not just low mood alongside psychosis",
